data.description: This charming Craftsman-style residence features a single-story layout and is fully prepared for your occupancy. Delight in leisurely moments on either the front porch or the rear patio. The third bedroom, accessible via French doors, can serve as a versatile space for either an office or a den, seamlessly connected to the living room. The primary suite offers a relaxing jetted tub, and there's a brand-new gas water heater for your convenience. The garage is located at the back of the property, accessible from the alley, ensuring a consistently inviting and fresh curb appeal. This home offers three bedrooms and two bathrooms.
